I welcome any and all feedback and patches. Fork at will!!

Here's a list of issues I have with the current implementation:

DRY violations - Code duplication between _setManagerAttributes and
_setConnectionAttributes as well as _getCache.

Doctrine attributes - Determine which of these are configurable on the
manager and connection levels.

